            "explanation": "匹配电阻 plays a critical role in maintaining signal integrity within a 总线网. By absorbing electromagnetic wave signal energy, these resistors prevent signal reflections that can cause interference and data corruption. The effectiveness of 匹配电阻 is directly tied to the proper functioning of the bus network, making them a crucial component in this topology. [Data: Entities (1129); Relationships (1295)]"
